From a3d6e49214ff1a81ab8b8e6962b6015392acb011 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jacob Moroni <jmoroni@google.com>
Date: Mon, 15 Dec 2025 22:51:02 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] irdma: Add support for shared UD credit pool

Added support for a shared UD credit pool. The credits are stored
in a table that is exposed as a shared memory segment in every
process that has the option enabled. This option is disabled by
default but can be enabled by setting:

IRDMA_SHARED_UD_CREDITS=X

Signed-off-by: Jacob Moroni <jmoroni@google.com>
